2 unit(s) Plant-Based Burger Patty
¾ cup Jasmine Rice
¼ cup Panko Breadcrumbs
113 g Baby Tomatoes
56 g Spring Mix
3 unit(s) Radish
2 tbsp Ketchup
1 tbsp Sesame Seeds
1 tbsp Seasoned Rice Vinegar
1 unit(s) Honey
1 tbsp Sesame Oil
1 tbsp Worcestershire Sauce
¼ tsp Salt*
0.13 tsp Pepper*

Once water is boiling, add rice, then reduce heat to low. Cover and cook until rice is tender and liquid is absorbed, 12-14 min.
Remove from heat. Set aside, still covered.
Meanwhile, halve tomatoes.
﻿Halve radishes lengthwise, then cut into thin half - moons.

Heat a large non-stick pan over medium-high heat.
When hot, add sesame seeds to the dry pan. Toast, stirring often, until golden, 3-4 min. (TIP: Keep your eye on them so they don't burn!)
Transfer sesame seeds to a plate.

Add Beyond Meat® patties, Panko, half the Worcestershire sauce, 1/4 tsp (1/2 tsp) salt to a medium bowl, then combine. Season with pepper.
Form mixture into 4 equal sized patties (8 patties for 4 ppl). (NOTE: Your mixture may look wet; this is normal! In step 3, you can carefully re-shape the patties when cooking.)

Reheat the same pan (from step 2) over medium-high.
When hot, add half the sesame oil, then Beyond Meat® patties. Pan-fry until cooked through, 3-4 min per side.**

Meanwhile, combine ketchup, remaining Worcestershire sauce, remaining honey and 3 tbsp (6 tbsp) water in a small bowl. (NOTE: This is your sauce to be used in the next step.)
Add vinegar, half the sesame seeds, half the honey and remaining sesame oil to a large bowl. Season with salt and pepper, then whisk to combine. (NOTE: This is your salad dressing!)
Add spring mix, radishes and tomatoes to the bowl with salad dressing, then toss to combine.

Reduce heat to medium-low.
Add prepared sauce (from step 5) to the pan. Cook, until sauce thickens slightly and Beyond Meat® patties are well coated, 1 min.
Remove from heat.
Fluff rice with a fork, then stir in remaining sesame seeds.
Divide rice, patties and salad between plates.
Spoon any remaining sauce over Beyond Meat® patties.

I f you've opted to get Beyond Meat®, cook patties the same way the recipe instructs you to cook the turkey patties.